reviewText: Laura Mckenzie Tahiti & French Polynesia Travel Tips is way better than Rand McNally South Seas Video Trip version!  If you want to go swimming beware natives goes topless!  If you are looking for A hotel that has history then you will like A hotel that is on A old sugar plantation that has rooms on stilts in the water that has A window in the floor that you can look out during the night and see the lights!  You will also learn about native dishes!  I grew up with this travel series as A kid!

In this movie you will learn about famous hotels and restaurants!  You will learn about historic churches and castles as well as A famous french palace!  In some cites in the French Riviera you will have to walk up many steps!  If you want to go swimming beware that the ladies that live there go topless!  I grew up with this travel series as A kid!

This movie just as good but maybe A little better than Rand McNally Caribbean Video Trip!  In this one Laura Mckenzie Caribbean Travel Tips you will learn different information then that Rand McNally has to offer!  You will learn about A historic restaurant and inn that was founded by A famous pirate, famous Caribbean dishes like conk shell and other dishes, you will also take trips to other islands as well!  Wow so much more fascinating information then Rand McNally!  I grew up with this travel series as A kid!

This movie had A lot of interesting information like A ghost town that you can see in action, A petting zoo called koala bear land where you can play and pet and feed A koala bear, kangaroo, and emos!  I grew up with this travel series as A kid!
I would highly recommend Laura McKenzie's Travel Tips Mexican Beaches over Rand McNally Mexican Beach Resorts Video Tour!
